#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: customs.php
msgid "Plogins Customs - EU Import Duty for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Plogins Customs - EU-Einfuhrzoll für WooCommerce"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: customs.php
msgid "https://plogins.com/plogins-customs/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/de/plogins-customs/"

#. Description of the plugin
#: customs.php
msgid ""
"Estimate and add the EU flat import duty (from 1 July 2026) as a clear "
"checkout line for parcels shipped into the EU from outside it."
msgstr ""
"Schätzt den pauschalen EU-Einfuhrzoll (ab 1. Juli 2026) und fügt ihn als "
"klare Checkout-Zeile für Pakete hinzu, die von außerhalb in die EU versendet"
" werden."

#. Author of the plugin
#: customs.php
msgid "WPPoland.com"
msgstr "WPPoland.com"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: customs.php
msgid "https://wppoland.com"
msgstr "https://wppoland.com"

#: customs.php:47
msgid ""
"Customs - EU Import Duty for WooCommerce requires WooCommerce to be active."
msgstr ""
"Customs - EU-Einfuhrzoll für WooCommerce erfordert, dass WooCommerce aktiv "
"ist."

#: src/Admin/ProductFields.php:33
msgid "Customs tariff code"
msgstr "Zolltarifnummer"

#: src/Admin/ProductFields.php:35
msgid ""
"Optional. Products sharing a code count as one EU import duty line. Leave "
"empty to group by category."
msgstr ""
"Optional. Produkte mit demselben Code zählen als eine EU-Einfuhrzollzeile. "
"Leer lassen, um nach Kategorie zu gruppieren."

#: src/Admin/ProductFields.php:36
msgid "e.g. 6109 (T-shirts)"
msgstr "z. B. 6109 (T-Shirts)"

#: src/Admin/ProUpsell.php:82
